    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;illusion&nbsp;(figment);\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;bard 2, sorcerer/wizard 2, witch 2;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)<br>\n    <strong>Area</strong>&nbsp;20-ft.-radius spread<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 round/level<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will disbelief (if interacted with);&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell creates the illusion of a translucent, ever-changing maze of glass in the target area. Creatures in the area who believe the maze to be real cannot move more than 5 feet continuously in any one direction and can't move diagonally, forcing them to take a circuitous route to their destination.</p>\n</div>\n",
